WEBVTT

00:01:58.750 --> 00:02:00.809
And they use the reflections
of these sounds

00:02:00.833 --> 00:02:02.559
to map the ground beneath.

00:02:02.583 --> 00:02:04.042
It can sound like this.

00:02:05.917 --> 00:02:10.583
(Explosion sounds)

00:02:11.875 --> 00:02:15.184
Then, there's the sound
of the actual drilling for oil and gas,

00:02:15.208 --> 00:02:18.393
the construction of things
like offshore wind farms,

00:02:18.417 --> 00:02:19.684
sonar

00:02:19.708 --> 00:02:23.726
and of course, the nearly constant drone
from more than 50,000 ships

00:02:23.750 --> 00:02:25.667
in the global merchant fleet.

00:02:26.792 --> 00:02:29.268
Now the natural ocean itself
isn't exactly quiet.

00:02:29.292 --> 00:02:31.059
If you put your head under the water,